This Act shall not apply to—
(a) the Western Province;
the Western Province;
(b) the Zambezi River;
the Zambezi River;
(c) the Luapula River;
the Luapula River;
(d) that portion of the Luangwa River which constitutes the boundary between Zambia and Mozambique.
