shall construct and maintain in repair—
(i) such bridges and other works as will make communication safe and convenient; and
such bridges and other works as will make communication safe and convenient; and
(ii) such culverts, aqueducts and other works as are necessary to secure the free circulation of such water or prevent interference with such mining;
